title: 836. Reaction to Kyler Murray's Contract Extension & Manning Passing Academy Takeaways
itunes:title: 836. Reaction to Kyler Murray's Contract Extension & Manning Passing Academy Takeaways
description:
Bucky Brooks and Rhett Lewis are back with a new episode of Move the Sticks. To start off, the guys react to the news of the Cardinals giving quarterback Kyler Murray a massive contract extension. Then, Rhett gives his takeaways from the Manning Passing Academy, while the pair focus on some talented college quarterbacks. To wrap up the show, the duo discuss a few quarterback training camp battles.


Move the Sticks is a part of the NFL Podcasts Network.
